<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-2301] QuorumPeer does not listen on passed client IP in the constructor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-2301</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;QuorumPeer does not listen on passed client IP in the constructor, for client  connection. It always listens on all IP(0.0.0.0 or 0:0:0:0:0:0:0:0). This happens only when QuorumPeer is created using any of the bellow constructors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;org.apache.zookeeper.server.quorum.QuorumPeer.QuorumPeer(Map&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Long&lt;/span&gt;,QuorumServer&amp;gt; quorumPeers, File snapDir,
            File logDir, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; clientPort, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; electionAlg,
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; myid, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; tickTime, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; initLimit, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; syncLimit)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;org.apache.zookeeper.server.quorum.QuorumPeer.QuorumPeer(Map&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Long&lt;/span&gt;,QuorumServer&amp;gt; quorumPeers, File snapDir,
            File logDir, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; clientPort, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; electionAlg,
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; myid, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; tickTime, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; initLimit, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; syncLimit,
            QuorumVerifier quorumConfig)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
